The main points to consider in the algorithm will be:

1. We should limit the search to exactly 64 steps.
2. We must avoid walking over the same spot more than once in the same path to achieve exactly 64 steps.
3. We cannot walk over rocks.
4. We need to count the number of unique positions we can reach.

